360	### Where errors are thrown
361	| Function | Condition | Error type |
362	|---|---|---|
363	| `updateCard` | `changes === 0` | `NotFoundError` |
364	| `deleteCard` | `changes === 0` | `NotFoundError` |
365	| `moveCard` | card not found | `NotFoundError` |
366	| `createComment` | FK violation | `ForeignKeyError` |
367	| `createComment` | other DB error | `DatabaseError` |
