154	```
155	
156	**Note**: Do NOT include `PRAGMA` statements in the SQL file. Pragmas are set programmatically in `initDb()` via `db.pragma()` before `db.exec()` is called. Mixing pragmas into migration SQL causes confusion and can misbehave if `db.exec` processes them in unexpected order.
