#### Describe: `deleteCard` (beforeEach: `initDb(':memory:')` then `createCard(...)`, afterEach: `closeDb()`)

```javascript
describe('deleteCard', () => {
  let cardId;
  beforeEach(() => {
    initDb(':memory:');
    cardId = createCard({ title: 'Delete me' }).id;
  });
  afterEach(() => closeDb());
  // ...tests...
