- `'updates title and returns the updated card'` — `updateCard(cardId, { title: 'New' })` → assert `updated.title === 'New'` and `updated.id === cardId`
- `'partial update does not modify unspecified fields'` — `updateCard(cardId, { title: 'Partial' })` → assert `updated.description === null` and `updated.column === 'ready'`
- `'can update multiple fields at once'` — `updateCard(cardId, { title: 'Multi', assignee: 'Bob', description: 'Desc' })` → assert all three updated
